modName: Weightless Axe and Reduced Firewood Weight
summary: Makes the Woodcutter's Axe weightless and reduces the weight of the Firewood to 1.
descriptionHtml: This mod makes the Woodcutter's Axe in Skyrim completely weightless and reduces the weight of the Firewood from 5 to 1.
